Lash Out.power: ion = The user lashes out to vent its frustration. Power is doubled if its stats dropped this turn.

Power Trip.power: ion = The user boasts of its strength. Power increases the more the user's stats are raised.

Aura Wheel.type: tion = Morpeko attacks and raises its Speed with energy stored in its cheeks. Type changes with the user's form.

Bolt Beak.power: ion = Stabs the target with an electrified beak. Power is doubled if the user attacks first.

Rising Voltage.power: ion = The user attacks with electric voltage rising from the ground. Power is doubled on Electric Terrain.

Misty Explosion.power: ion = The user attacks everything around and faints upon using this move. Power increases on Misty Terrain.

Body Press.power: ion = The user attacks by slamming its body into the target. Power increases the higher the user's Defense is.

Stomping Tantrum.power: ion = The user attacks driven by frustration. Power increases if the user's previous move failed.

Expanding Force.power: ion = The user attacks the target with psychic power. Powers up and hits all foes on Psychic Terrain.

Fishious Rend.power: ion = The user rends the target with its hard gills. Power doubles if the user moves first.

Barb Barrage.power: ion = Fires toxic barbs which may poison the target. Power is doubled if the target is poisoned.

Infernal Parade.power: ion = Hurls fireballs which may cause burns. Power is doubled if the target has a status condition.

Ivy Cudgel.type: tion = An ivy-wrapped cudgel strike with a high critical-hit ratio. Type changes based on the user's Mask.

Temper Flare.power: ion = The user attacks driven by frustration. Power increases if the user's previous move failed.
